sources.title: 1934 Csibi Der Fratz ( Franziska Gaal, Hermann Thimig, Tibor Von Halbay, Theo Lingen, Hans Richter, Anton Pointer)
sources.description: Film aus dem deutschen dritten Reich von 1934. Csibi der Fratz..  U.a mit Franziska Gaal und Hermann Thimig

metadata.Plot: No one suspects that Csibi, artistic name Lucie Carell, who is just taking a break after her last musical revue in Paris, has a good-looking mother back home who has just found an interesting suitor. When he knows about the daughter he mistakenly believes she is still a little girl, so when mother and daughter reunite Csibi is not going to disappoint him. Even if she likes his younger brother -very much.
metadata.Writer: Richard Eichberg, Régis Gignoux, Felix Jackson
metadata.Actors: Franciska Gaal, Leopoldine Konstantin, Herbert Hübner
